column5: Hi all,  Took the family out to a tiny local lake 5 minutes up the road for a calm evening relaxing and hopefully seeing the bobbers go down. Plan came together and the stress of the day was gone in the hour we spent out there together. Nothing fancy, jigs,minnows and slip bobbers with the big one going to the missus with a leech. Fish were on the edge of the weeds in 12' FOW.
Very nice   Doesn't get any more relaxing than that
I love my evening trips after work. Get home, have a quick dinner, and hit the water till dark o clock. - did it tonight. No better way to relax after a hot day at work!  S.
Great to fish with family thanks for the report

I love my evening trips after work. Get home, have a quick dinner, and hit the water till dark o clock. - did it tonight. No better way to relax after a hot day at work!  S.  Yup..  Did the same out on Gloucestor Pool lastnight with the oldman.  Lots of smallies on topwaters!
Awesome hour is you ask me...
